fields.title: Harris 1991 Health Professionals Survey, study no. 902070

dsDescription.dsDescriptionValue: This survey focuses on Nurses and Administrators about Health Care in America, Canada and Germany. Variables include satisfaction with health care system, quality of care and health services. Standard demographic variables are also included.
